Enhancements in v3.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  • WGS84 non-spherical Earth model with J2, J3, J4 harmonics
  • PREM dynamic density mapping
  • 3D trajectory integration framework
  • Expanded dataset (12+ flybys with archival mining)
  • Core raw DSN reanalysis with minimal OD (resolves Horizons circularity)
  • Hierarchical Bayesian model (addresses extreme heterogeneity)
  • Plasma modulation (addresses Cassini sign mismatch)
  • First-principles Temporal Shear Suppression calculation (reduces systematic uncertainty)
  • Bayesian model comparison with Bayes factors (statistical rigor)
